---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Editorial Policy" description="TechHub editorial policy and content standards." pageType="editorial-policy" showAds={false}>
  <article class="policy-page">
    <h1>Editorial Policy</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last updated: March 2026</p>

    <section>
      <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
      <p>We are committed to providing accurate, useful, and trustworthy content. Here's how we maintain quality:</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Content Standards</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Accuracy:</strong> We verify technical details and update content when needed.</li>
        <li><strong>Originality:</strong> We create original content or properly attribute sources.</li>
        <li><strong>Clarity:</strong> We explain technical concepts in accessible language.</li>
        <li><strong>Practicality:</strong> We focus on useful, actionable information.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Sources and References</h2>
      <p>We reference official documentation, reputable sources, and practical experience. For news, we link to original sources and provide original analysis.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Updates and Corrections</h2>
      <p>We review content periodically and update when information changes. If you spot an error, please <a href="/contact">let us know</a>.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Product Reviews and Recommendations</h2>
      <p>Our tool recommendations are based on genuine utility and quality, not promotional considerations. We disclose relationships when they exist.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>News Curation</h2>
      <p>We don't just aggregate news—we provide original summaries and explain why each story matters to developers and tech enthusiasts.</p>
    </section>
  </article>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .policy-page { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .policy-page h1 { margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm); }
  .last-updated { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.875rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl); }
  .policy-page section { margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl); }
  .policy-page h2 { font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md); color: var(--primary); }
  .policy-page ul { padding-left: var(--spacing-lg); }
  .policy-page li { margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm); }
  .policy-page a { color: var(--primary); }
</style>